{"type": "article", "id": 23931, "title": "铸铜的竹子家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-16T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135002aLmOnABSJTYuRyQ6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是由一个年轻的工作室设计的竹制家具，没有经过工业加工的竹子直接用做了结构，在竹节处绑上绳索，然后铸铜。有些地方使用了黑色的氧化层，黑色和金属色对比，表现出雕塑一样的古典感。每一根竹子的长短粗细和弯曲程度都不一样，是非常自然的状态，相互穿插时刻意增加了它的复杂，<a href=\"http://www.glithero.com/Les-french-extended-family\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134959ekJbTN9SzPIvhRit.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134959mugiHlwEd59oVCKn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135000o3jI7ZCrsOE2bmiK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213500069HinqoVAOP8GjDb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135001N89bCZo0vAUap4wg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}